ding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;The final tiny synthetic ray weighs 10g and is 16mm long.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;The cardiac cells had their DNA modified to be responsive to light.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;story-body__crosshead&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.2; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Chasing the light&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&quot;When we have a light in the front [of the ray], we activate an electrical signal in the tissue and it propagates like a wave through the musculature,&quot; explained Prof Parker.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&quot;You get this undulatory motion of the fins, and it looks as if it is chasing the light.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Each half of the robot is composed of different cardiac cells sensitive to specific light wavelengths.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;When picking one wavelength over the other, the scientists were able to steer the robot in a chosen direction.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Using this guidance system, the robotic ray was able to negotiate a simple obstacle course.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Researchers hope the robotic ray will help in the understanding of cardiac physiology.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&quot;We are making assumptions from our physiology textbooks that a heart beats the same way from every beat,&quot; Prof Parker told theÂ &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p002vsnb&quot; class=&quot;story-body__link&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); color: rgb(17, 103, 168); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.375; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: -webkit-focus-ring-color auto 5px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.298039);&quot;&gt;BBC World Service - Science in Action&lt;/a&gt;Â programme.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&quot;But if you talk to cardiovascular surgeons, they would tell no, it always beats differently.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;As a robot with a soft body, the ray is one of the first of its kind compared with other technologies that use rigid frames based on the gait of insects or mammals.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Another such robot is a jellyfish, developed by the same laboratory at the Wyss Institute in Boston.&lt;/p&gt;&quot;;i:3;s:10715:&quot;&lt;p&gt;sdnff dsfdjksnfds fdsnfdsf dsfnds fdsjfds fndsf dsf ds fds fds f df e d f ds fdf d Â fs das Â s Â sc dsf ds vds v f vf v f vf v f vfvdfv Â dfv df v dfv fd v dfv f v f vf dbdfb dfb dg b d bd b d b d vd sd Â ds Â s cs c s cs c s cds f rf Â f d f df d s Â w Â ds Â sd ds dfd sf&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;media-landscape no-caption full-width lead&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 32px; margin-right: -54.2188px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 16px; border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;image-and-copyright-container&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;js-image-replace&quot; alt=&quot;Robot stingray&quot; src=&quot;http://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/660/cpsprodpb/340B/production/_90332331_park3hr.jpg&quot; width=&quot;976&quot; height=&quot;549&quot; data-highest-encountered-width=&quot;660&quot; style=&quot;vertical-align: baseline; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto; max-width: 100%; -webkit-user-select: none; width: 645.781px; display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;off-screen&quot; style=&quot;color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px 1px 1px 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;&quot;&gt;Image copyright&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;story-image-copyright&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);&quot;&gt;HARVARD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;story-body__introduction&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 28px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.375; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Scientists have designed a robotic stingray that could help our understanding of the human heart.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 23px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;The miniature robot, one-tenth the scale of the actual fish, moves using heart cells taken from a rat.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Researchers hope the robotic ray will give new insight into the heart''s ability to pump blood and its potential implications in heart disease.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;The research is published in the journal,Â &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.sciencemag.org/&quot; class=&quot;story-body__link-external&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(34, 34, 34); border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.375; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.298039);&quot;&gt;Science&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&quot;It turns out the musculature in the stingray has to do the same thing as the heart does: it has to move fluids,&quot; said lead researcher, Prof Kevin Kit Parker of Harvard University, US.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;The scientists reverse-engineered the marine animal to understand how it glides in liquid environments.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;They then built a robotic prototype, which contains a gold skeleton and a single layer of 200,000 cardiac cells wrapped in a gel-like material similar to the gel used for breast implants.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;The final tiny synthetic ray weighs 10g and is 16mm long.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;The cardiac cells had their DNA modified to be responsive to light.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;story-body__crosshead&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); margin: 18px 0px 0px; font-size: 1.25rem; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Chasing the light&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&quot;When we have a light in the front [of the ray], we activate an electrical signal in the tissue and it propagates like a wave through the musculature,&quot; explained Prof Parker.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&quot;You get this undulatory motion of the fins, and it looks as if it is chasing the light.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Each half of the robot is composed of different cardiac cells sensitive to specific light wavelengths.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;When picking one wavelength over the other, the scientists were able to steer the robot in a chosen direction.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Using this guidance system, the robotic ray was able to negotiate a simple obstacle course.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Researchers hope the robotic ray will help in the understanding of cardiac physiology.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&quot;We are making assumptions from our physiology textbooks that a heart beats the same way from every beat,&quot; Prof Parker told theÂ &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p002vsnb&quot; class=&quot;story-body__link&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(17, 103, 168); border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.375; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: -webkit-focus-ring-color auto 5px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.298039);&quot;&gt;BBC World Service - Science in Action&lt;/a&gt;Â programme.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&quot;But if you talk to cardiovascular surgeons, they would tell no, it always beats differently.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;As a robot with a soft body, the ray is one of the first of its kind compared with other technologies that use rigid frames based on the gait of insects or mammals.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Another such robot is a jellyfish, developed by the same laboratory at the Wyss Institute in Boston.&lt;/p&gt;&quot;;}', '1468062367.jpg', '#A40778', 1468062368, 1, 'Admin', 2, 0);
